data.description: Motivated seller on this amazing double lot property! Over half an acre! Enjoy the 960 sq ft, 2 bedroom, 2 bath home, that has plenty of room for all the toys in the detached 2 car garage, RV/Boat carport, and more covered parking on the right side of the home and next to the garage. Also extra room to build more, or be subdivided. This home is being advertised with RV hook ups including water, electric, and sewer connections. Not all RVs or campers are compatible with the electric plug that is installed. Buyer to verify this during the inspection period time frame.
